{"type": "article", "id": 20501, "title": "木夹钱包", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-11T07:24:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101206Xt3MBGLcq2zO9SKg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款木制钱包，它有点类似于木头做的夹子。在两片方形木片中间有一块小的木片，形成了一个三角形结构，外面用一根皮筋栓住了两片木板，就可以依靠皮筋的弹力打开钱包。很简单，适合放名片和一些纸质零钱。钱包表面可以选择布面或者混凝土、金属铝等其他材料的图案。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210120454xu0qAjJchRgtSo.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101204GrWVQxmo6tHzc2Il.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101205GcrPSFAfewJk7K1O.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702101205dyec52W4vS96gqkT.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"742\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}